data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence featuring a versatile den/game room on the upper level. This property boasts an inviting open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas, complete with a cozy fireplace. The primary suite, conveniently located on the main floor, includes a stunning en-suite bathroom. Nestled in a serene, well-established neighborhood and within the highly regarded Clear Creek School District. This home is competitively priced, offering a fantastic opportunity to add your personal touches.
